Package: teems
Title: Trade and Environment Equilibrium Modeling System
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R:
    person("Matthew", "Cantele", , "matthew.cantele@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3729-1764"))
Description: A comprehensive modeling system for preparing and running all
    aspects of a Computable General Equilibrium (CGE) model. The package
    converts inputs, parses model files, calculates
    aggregation-specific parameter values, aggregates data to set
    specifications, compiles shocks and closures, and solves the model
    according to a wide range of parameters.
